CSAT_Score_1.label: CSAT_Score
CSAT_Score_1.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.SurveyQuestionResponse2.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by 'SurveyQuestion_QuestionType' == "Rating";q = filter q by 'SurveySubject_SubjectEntityType' == "LoyaltyProgram";Current = filter q by {{row(ActivityDate_1.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Year', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Month','SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Day')")}};Current = foreach Current generate 'Id' , 'SurveyVersion_SurveyId', 'SurveyVersionId', 'QuestionId', first('QuestionChoice_MaxValue') as 'Max Rating', first('NumberValue')/(first('QuestionChoice_MaxValue')) as 'Rating',first('SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime') as 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime', first('NumberValue') as 'NumberValue', first('Scale') as 'Scale','SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Year', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Month', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Day';Previous = filter q by {{row(ActivityDate_2.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Year', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Month', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Day')")}};Previous = foreach Previous generate 'Id' , 'SurveyVersion_SurveyId', 'SurveyVersionId', 'QuestionId', first('QuestionChoice_MaxValue') as 'Max Rating', first('NumberValue')/(first('QuestionChoice_MaxValue')) as 'PreviousRating',first('SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime') as 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime', first('NumberValue') as 'NumberValue', first('Scale') as 'Scale','SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Year', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Month', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Day';result = group Current by all full, Previous by all;result = foreach result generate coalesce(round((sum(Current.'Rating') * first(Current.'Scale'))/count(Current),2),0) as 'CSAT_Current',coalesce(round((sum(Previous.'PreviousRating') * first(Previous.'Scale'))/count(Previous),2),0) as 'CSAT_Previous';result = foreach result generate 'CSAT_Current','CSAT_Previous',('CSAT_Current' - 'CSAT_Previous')/'CSAT_Previous' as 'Delta',case when CSAT_Current < 0 then "rgb(232, 67, 64)" else "rgb(58, 232, 103)" end as 'Bar_Color_CSAT';

lens_4.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.SurveyQuestionResponse2.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by 'SurveyQuestion_QuestionType' == "Rating";q = filter q by 'SurveySubject_SubjectEntityType' == "LoyaltyProgram";q = foreach q generate 'Id' , 'SurveyVersion_SurveyId', 'SurveyVersionId', 'QuestionId', first('QuestionChoice_MaxValue') as 'Max Rating', first('SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime') as 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime', first('NumberValue') as 'NumberValue', first('Scale') as 'Scale','SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Year', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Month', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Day';result = foreach q generate  (sum(q.'NumberValue')/sum(q.'Max Rating')) * first(q.'Scale') as 'CSATValue', count(q) as 'count';result = group result by all;result = foreach result generate round(sum(CSATValue)/sum(count),2) as 'Program_CSAT';
